cargotable.description:
```js
cargotable {
  ID [, ID]*
}
```
The cargotable is a list of 4-byte long IDs or literal strings. Please see the list of cargo labels (https://newgrf-specs.tt-wiki.net/wiki/CargoTypes#Cargo_Labels) for the currently defined cargo labels and their cargo classes.
